{"tid":754979,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"中國寶成鐵路大搶修　實拍高溫下的擔山人","createTime":"2018-07-25T00:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T03:52:32.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3d0a96f3b7f48aaf71f8e368fef8f672d82aeb","tid":754979,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic2.dwnews.net/20180724/f93e0d86631cb89b9a60ace12b455606_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic2.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Ff93e0d86631cb89b9a60ace12b455606_w.jpg&h=96d38c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年7月23日，寶成鐵路山體崩塌搶險工作進入第11天。中國鐵路西安局集團有限公司已組織1,100余人，7台挖掘機、2台破石機對山體進行刷方減載，對中部錯落體和坡面浮石進行人工清方。&ldquo;擔山工&rdquo;每天都要挑著水泥和沙子從山腳搬到山上，就是為搶險過程中對刷方後的坡面進行&ldquo;噴漿&rdquo;所備。<img src=\"http://pic8.dwnews.net/20180724/9a4b5ec08110e160c528f09dd5ffd59d_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic8.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F9a4b5ec08110e160c528f09dd5ffd59d_w.jpg&h=f84ef882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擔山人不僅僅要背水泥上去，山上刷方噴漿、安裝封閉網等所需要的沙子、鋼筋、鋼管、架板、封閉網以及山上爆破需要的炸藥，都是擔山人一個肩膀一個肩膀的往山上扛。截至目前，他們已經為山上&ldquo;噴漿&rdquo;施工提供了10余噸水泥。<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic5.dwnews.net/20180724/449e269c3b788827ea891d19b98ae999_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic5.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F449e269c3b788827ea891d19b98ae999_w.jpg&h=7af37d2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於山上沒有路，上山必須途徑的一個陡坡，幾乎是直上直下，除了用手抓著安全繩，還需要手扶著山上的石頭或者草根，擔山工肩膀扛著沈甸甸的水泥，脖子上的青筋繃起，幾乎是用整個身體把水泥往上托。<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic8.dwnews.net/20180724/ceb683683d9104a4dcc240360f52f654_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic8.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Fceb683683d9104a4dcc240360f52f654_w.jpg&h=1cb27cbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擔山工在往山上搬運搶險物資和器具。<img src=\"http://pic2.dwnews.net/20180724/730a1d98e986a597f92fb0a31fbd3cd2_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic2.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F730a1d98e986a597f92fb0a31fbd3cd2_w.jpg&h=f2b646fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n擔山工頭頂烈日、肩負重物，正往山上運送物資。<img src=\"http://pic6.dwnews.net/20180724/5588fba0b962b250197f6ae0b615532f_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic6.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F5588fba0b962b250197f6ae0b615532f_w.jpg&h=509fd9e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶成鐵路山體崩塌搶險施工現場。<img src=\"http://pic7.dwnews.net/20180724/a746e4a85ff764fa0316d2ba691230d1_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic7.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Fa746e4a85ff764fa0316d2ba691230d1_w.jpg&h=1eb075a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人們合力將油桶擡上車。<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic3.dwnews.net/20180724/c21db774f5f5965c5d72f01c92e236db_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic3.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Fc21db774f5f5965c5d72f01c92e236db_w.jpg&h=33760a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在炎炎烈日下，工人們合力擡起一個油桶。<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic9.dwnews.net/20180724/f4a51846d28c2fb201f1792552c9c11f_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic9.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Ff4a51846d28c2fb201f1792552c9c11f_w.jpg&h=5917fa1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前，寶成線略陽至樂素河間塌方搶險現場，共計有擔山工160名，他們是山上物資的傳輸者，是搶險中最低調的那群&ldquo;英雄&rdquo;。<img src=\"http://pic2.dwnews.net/20180724/14946ead0de041ca0e1681cb2ad073f8_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic2.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F14946ead0de041ca0e1681cb2ad073f8_w.jpg&h=5a5d11ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年7月20日，搶險人員在寶成鐵路山體崩塌搶險現場進行作業。<img src=\"http://pic2.dwnews.net/20180724/8ce3a5925d97087c182f593e8bdc0b79_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic2.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F8ce3a5925d97087c182f593e8bdc0b79_w.jpg&h=8ac5347e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搶險人員使用大型機具在寶成鐵路山體崩塌現場山上清理松動土體和危石。<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic7.dwnews.net/20180724/8fc8a446fdd633138e4a3bc3d6dc9afd_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic7.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F8fc8a446fdd633138e4a3bc3d6dc9afd_w.jpg&h=f5d784da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年7月18日，搶險人員在寶成鐵路王家沱至樂素河間山體崩塌現場清理松動土體和危石。<img src=\"http://pic3.dwnews.net/20180724/cb2d020e5eb00767815d7a34772a5c83_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic3.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Fcb2d020e5eb00767815d7a34772a5c83_w.jpg&h=aeed7d1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶成鐵路搶險第6天，工人吊在百米懸崖上清理危石。2018年7月18日，已累計清理塌體19,400立方米，修建950米的施工便道。<img src=\"http://pic5.dwnews.net/20180724/1e6accdba0ab94d9d56dd3f6152a65de_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic5.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F1e6accdba0ab94d9d56dd3f6152a65de_w.jpg&h=eb7d3f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年7月17日，寶成鐵路陝西略陽段王家沱至樂素河間山體崩塌搶險現場。<img src=\"http://pic4.dwnews.net/20180724/a883df30591f542fa2da5438d854a01d_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic4.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Fa883df30591f542fa2da5438d854a01d_w.jpg&h=de8e66b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搶險人員使用挖掘機在寶成鐵路陝西略陽段王家沱至樂素河間山體崩塌現場清理塌方體。<img src=\"http://pic5.dwnews.net/20180724/388047313e95c6792ed54a1f8fd164dd_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic5.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F388047313e95c6792ed54a1f8fd164dd_w.jpg&h=0a7faedf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搶險人員在寶成鐵路陝西略陽段王家沱至樂素河間山體崩塌現場搬運搶險物資。<img src=\"http://pic8.dwnews.net/20180724/6c5105c960e6dbe975e235120d116e4b_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic8.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F6c5105c960e6dbe975e235120d116e4b_w.jpg&h=31ecdaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年7月16日，寶成鐵路陝西略陽段王家沱至樂素河間山體崩塌搶險現場。<img src=\"http://pic4.dwnews.net/20180724/fcb82c06aad7a678ef75c3f1650d99e3_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic4.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Ffcb82c06aad7a678ef75c3f1650d99e3_w.jpg&h=0e6fe36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶成鐵路山體崩塌搶險現場，工人們正在搭建施工便道。<img src=\"http://pic7.dwnews.net/20180724/ad9ef2d6428895c847e58a02ef5b3439_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic7.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2Fad9ef2d6428895c847e58a02ef5b3439_w.jpg&h=86c999a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寶成鐵路陝西略陽段王家沱至樂素河間山體崩塌搶險現場。<img src=\"http://pic8.dwnews.net/20180724/00c6904ce1c67d9cb66aeb72d3a96b83_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic8.dwnews.net%2F20180724%2F00c6904ce1c67d9cb66aeb72d3a96b83_w.jpg&h=4d9da8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年7月12日晚至13日7時，寶成鐵路陝西略陽縣王家沱至樂素河區間連續發生山體塌方災害，塌方體總量約75,000立方米，將白雀寺隧道口掩埋，約100余米鐵路線被土石覆蓋。<br />\n.<br />\n編輯：葉昆石<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.dwnews.com/china/big5/photo/2018-07-24/60072791.html#p=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.dwnews.com%2Fchina%2Fbig5%2Fphoto%2F2018-07-24%2F60072791.html%23p%3D20&d=%2B7Pt3pkRVvoFF7tiJgRHYB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=4c24cebf\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.dwnews.com/china/big5/photo/2018-07-24/60072791.html#p=20</a>"},{"pid":"e49cd5ab16e475554223dd1540834bfa2e3d07ae","tid":754979,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:03:03.000Z","msg":"厲害了 他的國"},{"pid":"3b588ebc2b5edd118a3c906016a519b5583cb1d6","tid":754979,"uid":176472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:11:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">整完一樣塌到仆街陷家隡，<br />\n<br />\n同啲港女着 bra top 上山自拍打咭有乜分別？</span>"},{"pid":"abd3c1092be82f1a89a10e91773bcf54f49ccc84","tid":754979,"uid":22876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:13:03.000Z","msg":"領道: 白事當做紅事辦"},{"pid":"241cc28ac8a4a229b36c13494894df29b6787e97","tid":754979,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T00:40:36.000Z","msg":"仲係中文黎？"},{"pid":"8fdd508ed5c84982046ecb90dcd541a4261fb9ce","tid":754979,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"同英國保誠有冇關係？"}]}